  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Ve-cadherin is expressed in endothelial cells. Systemic slerosis is a rare auto-immune
      disease with a endothelial dysfunction. This study is to evaluated the level of soluble
      VE-cadherin and VE-cadherin antibody in patients with systemic slerosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
